---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABand from '@/components/CTABand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Travel Insurance | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Travel insurance for residents and visitors to Canada. Get peace of mind for your next trip with coverage arranged through Heidi Blondin Financial."
>

  <section class="bg-brand-plum py-20">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow-light mb-5">Insurance</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-white text-balance" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Travel Insurance</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-6" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Why do I need Travel Insurance?</h2>
      <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>Sudden illnesses, accidents and theft can instantly turn your fun vacation into a financial nightmare. Don't let your travel plans be ruined by an unforeseen event. Travel Insurance offers you peace of mind so you can enjoy your hard earned vacation.</p>
        <p>Carrying insurance when you travel provides the comfort of knowing that if you break your arm or your luggage is stolen, all of the expenses are covered. That way, you can focus on your family instead of worrying about how you're going to afford medical bills or new clothes and other travel essentials.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary-gold">Get Your Travel Package Today</a>
      </div>

      <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4 mt-12">
        <p>At Heidi Blondin Financial Inc. we are pleased to provide you with comprehensive travel insurance from various insurance carriers. Whether you're a resident, or visiting from another country, and traveling to Canada for business or for leisure, consider purchasing travel insurance before you begin your trip.</p>
        <p>The process is simple, you can get quotes and apply online. Contact Heidi to find the best solution for you.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary-gold">Buy Now</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary-plum">Contact Heidi Today</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABand heading="Travel with confidence" sub="Book a free consultation and we'll make sure you're covered before your next trip." />

</BaseLayout>
